{"tid":1458364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔割𥱊]持久戰先會贏 唔好再指責機場走既人","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:48:30.000Z","uid":290611,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"73e6632ac7a21d052af607f0047c3def0628ef29","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:47:06.000Z","msg":"唔好再指責機場走既人，係五點幾個陣，無人知道之後會發生咩事，當時又公布班機取消曬，再留守落去都唔知會係結果。但有一樣野我地要記住，就係我地今次打既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰，只有長期戰才可以造成更大既影響</span></strong></span>，人地韓國用左半年先拉到朴謹惠落台，韓國仲要係民選總統，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我們一定要唔割𥱊，常駐機場，同對家鬥長命</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外一樣就係知己知彼，中共就是靠文宣起家，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣都非常重要</span></strong></span>，老毛係《論持久戰》一書中就講到：民族革命戰爭無普遍和深入既政治動員，是不能勝利的，我地都要拉攏多d 淺藍，實際將我地既目的話畀佢地聽，盡力爭取最多既支持，先可以齊心一致對抗對家！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知已知彼，百戰不殆。我地要贏，就要熟悉對家既玩法，老毛當年閉關睇左勁多書先後尾可以用咁多齷齪既手段上位，如果我地可以睇通老毛啲書知道點玩咁我地贏面就會大啲，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地有勇，但我地亦都要有謀</span></strong></span>，歡迎討論（戰術策略等討論都歡迎）！！"},{"pid":"ba12de5310e694e73558fc04757f08b1db323882","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"自推十式"},{"pid":"9188d60f841cd26fd89d03f74744963d962e42ef","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"b17d8c0431f2bb1a29a3964656251ff092c474a3","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:50:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"add6f555ef2388cd989204bf2fb44e7f1970919c","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"29a1560aaecfe5296f13e0a087093a65f5880586","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:50:45.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"fda535fc8820d9ec7039cb151f140fb51ccb6fd4","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:53:26.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"4cc058ea95e3cab64e5482bd865e3472fb6b4a91","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"4fd625124d2c105bc4e14483ef184be4a89fac21","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"777"},{"pid":"f3fdc464a130762d216f2706fb27cb4b7344698c","tid":1458364,"uid":3456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f60d3ffda0ecfc2dc1fef38f6e8f15a60f3eac7","tid":1458364,"uid":222333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:13:20.000Z","msg":"認同，我都有份叫人走，而家睇返機場無事發生，我認係錯估左形勢<br />\n<br />\n但一開頭大家揀機場做集會原意就係想減低損失，留守無疑係比較有風險既選擇"},{"pid":"240da27b493189044d703e6cc5ba1ddc7ef12ebe","tid":1458364,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"------------------<br />\nAndroid 版Airdrop：Files by Google<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457044</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ffac871be3e30394a5fec13eb628a4a79340af6a","tid":1458364,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f60d3ffda0ecfc2dc1fef38f6e8f15a60f3eac7","tid":1458364,"uid":222333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:13:20.000Z","msg":"認同，我都有份叫人走，而家睇返機場無事發生，我認係錯估左形勢<br />\n<br />\n但一開頭大家揀機場做集會原意就係想減低損失，留守無疑係比較有風險既選擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得警察 同埋市民陷入互相評估嘅狀態<br />\n 即係所有消息都 有利於力量較強嘅一方"},{"pid":"c62eed017a514c2f73bebf6655f19d7786eea512","tid":1458364,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"fbb9dc13ed01e032a8c6cbfda481a824e5ce5006",